data.text:
Hana, I'm currently
                      teaching English as a Second Language, and I love
                      for my students to get confident in producing
                      English or increasing their listening ability. I
                      know that you speak English as a second language,
                      but you do such an amazing job and it's inspiring
                      to me, so I love my students to improve and like
                      it, and so because you're a perfect example, what
                      are some strategies you have for my students so I
                      could tell them?
